    "sn1.61:0.2": "Addhavagga → anvavaggo (bj); andhavaggo (sya-all, pts2ed) ",
    "sn1.61:1.1": "addhabhavi → anvabhavi (bj); andhabhavi (sya-all) ",
    "sn1.61:1.4": "vasamanvagū”ti → vasamaddhagū (mr) "
  },
